# Claude Code config — fully local. The harness auto-writes permission
# additions to settings.json every time a new path is approved, which
# clutters GitHub Desktop each session. Matches readers-gnt (commit 4af66ce)
# and readers-bofm gitignore policy.
.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json

